{"tid":1394407,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［恐嚇公務員］來睇下政府點樣搬龍門","createTime":"2019-08-01T11:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:58:42.000Z","uid":128430,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aeea2fd9c25c0a9d9d2ec57b9dfcf7ea3809932b","tid":1394407,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">公務員事務局出嘅聲明當然話你班公務員同政府「對著幹」，又話你地政治集會，恐嚇埋嚴肅處理</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yawuOLS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyawuOLS.png&h=ec663dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地又睇下幾日前，偉大嘅警察員佐級協會講左啲咩！佢哋對政府第二把膠椅、政務司司長予以最嚴厲譴責。政府從未話佢地同政府「對著幹」，從未話過佢地啲政治聲明有違政治中立</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/euffKmV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeuffKmV.png&h=a0b76763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">又睇下五月果陣發生咩事。幾個公務員出聲明支持修訂逃犯條例，仲教立法會做野，夠政治啦啩</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgKDG9F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgKDG9F.png&h=fbcb2ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當時政府話：<span style=\"color: red;\">逃犯條例修訂不涉及政治問題，而是政策問題，公務員支持是無可厚非，亦是合情合理，不存在影響其政治中立。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y03Ufvh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY03Ufvh.png&h=901785c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">睇到呢度，請問個標準係邊度？龍門擺明任係佢擺嘅！越恐嚇我地越要支持公務員行出來！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">八月二日公務員集會</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">八月五日全港三罷</span>"},{"pid":"ef932dc69c15d445ba96983a5ac82711ed3d2b44","tid":1394407,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"}]}